[Name] Fast Lexical Analyzer Generator
[Summary] A tool for generating text-scanning programs.
[License] BSD License (revised)
[Description] Flex is a tool for generating programs that recognize \
lexical patterns in text. There are many applications for Flex, \
including writing compilers in conjunction with GNU Bison. Flex is a \
free implementation of the well known Lex program. It features a Lex \
compatibility mode, and also provides several new features such as \
exclusive start conditions.
[Homepage] https://flex.sourceforge.net/
